### AI Booking System - API Tests
### Use Ctrl+Shift+P -> "Rest Client: Send Request" or click "Send Request" above each request

@baseUrl = https://ai-booking-mvp.onrender.com
@localUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### Get Client Configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/clients/stay-focused-fitness-chris

###

### Get Client Events/Appointments  
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/stay-focused-fitness-chris

###

### Integration Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/integration-health

###

### Get Leads for Client
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/leads?clientKey=stay-focused-fitness-chris

###

### Get Calls for Client
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calls?clientKey=stay-focused-fitness-chris

###

### Test Local Development (when server running locally)
GET {{localUrl}}/api/clients/stay-focused-fitness-chris

###

### Create Test Lead (POST example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientKey": "stay-focused-fitness-chris",
  "name": "Test Lead",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "source": "API Test"
}

###

### Book Appointment (POST example)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/book-appointment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientKey": "stay-focused-fitness-chris",
  "leadId": "123",
  "datetime": "2025-11-25T10:00:00Z",
  "service": "Consultation"
}


